quadrant = ci_frame.FrameGeometry.euclid_bottom_left()
quadrant_rotated = quadrant.rotate_before_serial_cti(image_pre_clocking=
    quadrant_data)
quadrant_rotated_back = quadrant.rotate_after_serial_cti(image_post_clocking
    =quadrant_rotated)
assert (quadrant_rotated_back == quadrant_data).all()
